title: Single South Korean women carry dehydrated fox vaginas
text: Share this article Share The female shaman told her 'it has the power to attract people and it will help you get a man.' Kim, who manages a beef and pork importing company, has been on several blind dates with no luck. She also feels tired from work and suffers digestive problems. She told Al Jazeera : 'The shaman told me the cause of all of my problems was that I don't have a boyfriend. One woman named Kim Min-Kyeong carries the small genitalia in a pouch everywhere she goes 'I was advised to keep it with me at all times for one year and to never remove it from its bag, or else it would lose its strength. 'I was going through such a tough time that I really wanted to believe in it, I was emotionally vulnerable.' Kim, who has a month left before the power of her amulet runs out, said it makes her feel more confident. She said she goes out more and has made more friends. But it remains to be seen whether her lucky charm will deliver her a boyfriend. Read more: Share or comment on this article 9
